reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Bright as expected!
reviews.reviewText: These were an excellent choice for my wife's car. She has been complaining that her original bulbs made it hard to see at night while driving. These were the answer to her concerns. I would buy these again and recommend to anyone

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Got them for my 2009 Honda Civic. They work great! I can see so much further now. Included image is of the old halogen on the passenger side and the new LED on the driver side. Installation on the passenger side was a pain (I'm not used to changing the lights myself), but it's got nothing to do with the LEDs themselves, had ti follow a YouTube video tutorial to access to the bulb. Once I had them both on, they worked amazingly. Took the car to a part of town with no streetlights after dark, and the difference between the old bulbs and the new was vast! Package comes with 4 bulbs, 2 for low beams and 2 for high beams (1 pair on each side). Make sure the models fit on your car, and then order them ASAP. You won't be disappointed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A lot brighter than stock
reviews.reviewText: Send great so far, they are a lot brighter than the stock headlights. Only downside is the blinking DRL indicator on the dash but that's easily ignored and does not show error the headlights are on. Let's see how long the bulbs last.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are nice and brighter than the OEM ones that came on my 2012 Corolla S but the DRL lights flicker a lot... When the headlights are turned on, they flicker as well but not as bad or as often as the DRLs do. I bought two orders just in case the first order was defective but the second order had the same issue. I'd say it's worth the price if you don't mind that issue but I'd rather not deal with that since it can be distracting not only to you but to other drivers while driving.

reviews.reviewText: when they say led headlights are brighter then standard headlights, they are absolutely right. i love them, so as longevity well i dont know cause i just got them , but my trailer has led lights and they are 4 yrs old and work perfect.
